  <brief_title>Autologous Implantation of Mesenchymal Stem Cells for the Treatment of Distal Tibial Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Autologous Implantation of Mesenchymal Stem Cells for the Treatment of Distal Tibial Fractures</official_title>
